Oat Cake Recipe
* 200g porridge oats
* 1 tsp salt
* 1 tsp cracked black pepper
* 50ml extra virgin olive oil
* A little boiling water

Blend half oats + salt & pepper (medium fine); 
add rest of oats & mix
Pour in Oil & stir a bit
Add 2-3 tbsp boiling water - form soft dough
Knead for 30 seconds
Roll to 5mm thick & cut
